<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.4">
<l>paṇṇulām meṉmoḻip pāvaimār paṇaimulai yaṇaitum nāmeṉ</l>
<l>ṟeṇṇuvā reṇṇama toḻittunī piḻaittuyyak karuti ṉāyēl</l>
<l>viṇṇuḷār viṇṇiṉmī tiyaṉṟavēṅ kaṭattuḷār vaḷaṅkoḷ munnīr</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṉār vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you intend to be saved, escaping, shunning the thoughts of those who think,</l>
<l>“We will embrace the full breasts of ladies whose soft voices are like music,”</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ,</l>
<l rend="indent">[the city of] the one the hue of the beautiful three-watered [sea],</l>
<l>Who is in heaven, [and] who is on Vēṅkaṭa [Mountain]</l>
<l rend="indent">which reaches higher than heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
